<pb n="0147b" xml:id="I01.0057.0147b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0147b01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0147b0101">大齊天保五年歲次甲戌四月丙辰朔
<lb ed="I" n="0147b02"/>二日丁巳。　天宮頌<app type="star" corresp="#0147004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">文</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">攵</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0147b03"/>夫<note n="0147005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30833"/>＝至【史】</note><note n="0147005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30833"/>【佛拓】，至【史】</note><app n="0147005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">至</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30833"/></rdg></app>道沖靜。必資物以顯真。沈隱留像。
<lb ed="I" n="0147b04"/>因阿難以存形。須達捨金。感群迷以就
<lb ed="I" n="0147b05"/>正。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear>以邑儀人等。故知大慈異興。<note n="0147006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB03850"/>＝閻【史】</note><note n="0147006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB03850"/>【佛拓】，閻【史】</note><app n="0147006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">閻</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB03850"/></rdg></app>浮
<lb ed="I" n="0147b06"/>難<note n="0147007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB20060"/>＝處【史】</note><note n="0147007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB20060"/>【佛拓】，處【史】</note><app n="0147007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB20060"/></rdg></app>。磬竭家珍。敬崇三寶。造二寶塔。石
<lb ed="I" n="0147b07"/>像三區。上為　皇帝<note n="0147008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30834"/>＝永【史】</note><note n="0147008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30834"/>【佛拓】，永【史】</note><app n="0147008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">永</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30834"/></rdg></app>隆。百官朝慶。法
<lb ed="I" n="0147b08"/>　界有形。咸同斯<note n="0147009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30779"/>＝願【史】</note><note n="0147009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30779"/>【佛拓】，願【史】</note><app n="0147009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30779"/></rdg></app>。其詞曰　金柱一
<lb ed="I" n="0147b09"/>振。万侶俱張。同茲<app type="star" corresp="#0147002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30838"/></rdg></app>法。眾惠<note n="0147b0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【佛拓】【史】</note><app n="0147b0901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】 【史】">旡</rdg></app>常。一階
<lb ed="I" n="0147b10"/>超九。<app type="star" corresp="#0147008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">永</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30834"/></rdg></app>誤時亡。殊山寶石。異想神功。誤
<lb ed="I" n="0147b11"/>斯應狀。動現真容。虛來異顯。滅去難蹤。
<lb ed="I" n="0147b12"/>光明主任僧惠　齋主暢洛生
<lb ed="I" n="0147b13"/>頂生王主樊安欣孫顯和邑子張明堂
<lb ed="I" n="0147b14"/>供養主蔡元興邑老郭懷邑子<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">呂</unclear>　姬
<lb ed="I" n="0147b15"/>邑主葉容　邑子邢祖暈邑子常元姜
<lb ed="I" n="0147b16"/>邑主暢<app type="star" corresp="#0147003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30835"/></rdg></app>　邑子孫貴和邑子董慶族
<lb ed="I" n="0147b17"/>都維<note n="0147010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30839"/>＝那【史】</note><note n="0147010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30839"/>【佛拓】，那【史】</note><app n="0147010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30839"/></rdg></app>張甑邑子<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"><app type="star" corresp="#0147006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">閻</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB03850"/></rdg></app></unclear>黑　邑子古薩寶
<lb ed="I" n="0147b18"/>都維<app type="star" corresp="#0147010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30839"/></rdg></app>張璨邑子　　　邑子董伏和
<lb ed="I" n="0147b19"/>維<app type="star" corresp="#0147010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30839"/></rdg></app>郭外生邑子張法悅邑子卜陽買
<lb ed="I" n="0147b20"/>維<app type="star" corresp="#0147010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30839"/></rdg></app>梁市買邑子<note n="0147011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB08670"/>＝曹【史】</note><note n="0147011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB08670"/>【佛拓】，曹【史】</note><app n="0147011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">曹</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB08670"/></rdg></app>漫　邑子邵荊瑤
<lb ed="I" n="0147b21"/>維<app type="star" corresp="#0147010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30839"/></rdg></app>魏僧化邑子段迴軍邑子王康
<lb ed="I" n="0147b22"/>中正□珍和邑子張胡奴邑子梁榮國
<lb ed="I" n="0147b23"/>中正孫張霸邑子卜<note n="0147012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02462"/>＝虎【史】</note><note n="0147012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02462"/>【佛拓】，虎【史】</note><app n="0147012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02462"/></rdg></app>　邑子卜清醜
<lb ed="I" n="0147b24"/>　　　　　邑子<app type="star" corresp="#0147011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">曹</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB08670"/></rdg></app><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">郎</unclear>仁邑子楊黑
<lb ed="I" n="0147b25"/>　　　　　邑子□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">延</unclear>慶邑<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">子</unclear>□□□</p></cb:div></cb:div>
